Jean-Louis Trintignant https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Louis_Trintignant 0 Jean-Louis Xavier Trintignant (French pronunciation: ​[tʁɛ̃tiɲɑ̃]; born 11 December 1930) is a retired French actor. He won the Best Actor Award at the 1969 Cannes Film Festival as well as the Best Actor Award at the César Awards 2013. Jean-Louis_Xavier_Trintignant ( French_pronunciation : [_tʁɛ̃tiɲɑ̃_] ; born_11_December_1930 ) is a_retired_French_actor .
